{"tid":226871,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"隻貓身上生滿勁多黑色一點點嘅嘢","createTime":"2017-05-02T19:08:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-03T19:35:42.000Z","uid":96071,"like":3,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0ed8998f262f44011e538fac7c5eb9135d774e4c","tid":226871,"uid":96071,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T19:08:17.000Z","msg":"幫frd問<br />\n佢近排同隻貓玩嗰陣發現佢身上啲毛有啲黑色嘢<br />\n跟著佢就撥開嚟睇 一掂隻黑色嘢就走得勁快<br />\n之後就開始發現越來越多 仲要每次都好多黑色點圍住隻嘢<br />\n其實係咪跳虱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有幫隻貓沖涼有滴藥水 但都仲係咁<br />\n宜家就連佢張床都有勁多呢啲黑色嘢<br />\n仔細睇會見到啲嘢識蠕動 好恐佈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當我個frd用酒精抹啲黑色嘢會嗰陣佢地會好似識流血咁變成紅色<br />\n隻貓去過嘅地方都會有佢地嘅痕跡<br />\n有無人知係咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：我朋友養左兩隻貓，兩隻都有呢個問題<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1658134.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1658134.jpg&h=4bd28033&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0420d719eca050540ab94fb378fc4d4aed869b70","tid":226871,"uid":96071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T19:13:58.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"191475bf54584dfdffb05470d4fdb8b25367b28f","tid":226871,"uid":14716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T19:14:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a9a0eacad73526b7053f2a982d089a923108a88","tid":226871,"uid":68202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T19:15:03.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"da0a956e34d37027fc7c578f37dca923e2562554","tid":226871,"uid":14716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T19:15:47.000Z","msg":"啲血係咪貓血嚟㗎<br />\n<br />\n黑色嘢嚟咗貓血"},{"pid":"1bdf10ee15e4567eba9d1fc3acfae3c1df09d391","tid":226871,"uid":20494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc