9863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T20:52:45.000Z","msg":"我兩隻貓上年都有蚤 長期戰鬥咗半年先消失晒<br />\n仲要正常貓蚤唔咬人 要唔知多到點先會咬人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n全屋人都唔咬 就係咬我 咬到我有陰影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbf647d67481749d7ee904342db27e61b6bdaa9f","tid":226871,"uid":560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T21:00:12.000Z","msg":"前幾年有過一次 兩隻貓同時有<br />\n即時幫佢地沖涼加滴蚤水 好快就冇事"},{"pid":"708fd1f724c94793f6c9d0674eb698fbd2b933f2","tid":226871,"uid":65354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T21:26:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>貓蝨。。。貓貓幾大？？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n4歲了</blockquote><br />\n點解唔幫佢定期滴revolution??  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢話佢有定期滴 發現左之後都有滴</blockquote><br />\n有滴都搞成咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我果隻日日出街去草叢爬樹又唔肯沖涼都冇野 <br />\n係咪你friend成日唔記得滴或者嫌貴冇keep咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"149f013d49df3c7ad3d1ed9a980e979a41dbcbd5","tid":226871,"uid":83585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T21:30:42.000Z","msg":"啲黑色一點點應該唔係跳虱<br />\n但行得好快果啲就係 <br />\n你望清楚啲黑色一點點應該係唔識郁嘅<br />\n係虱啲屎黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一抹會變磚紅色<br />\n證明隻貓身上真係有好多虱"},{"pid":"38f9a1e32198005ec218890303fff91f81d0e7d3","tid":226871,"uid":9863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T21:33:02.000Z","msg":"其實係咪應該長期keep住滴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f56bbe7bcf1b55f422938872a8b3fbc23fa1911","tid":226871,"uid":50275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T21:34:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實係咪應該長期keep住滴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n想知，同問"},{"pid":"22911094f36385fed549f2c08b2b03a37086e1cd","tid":226871,"uid":83585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T21:34:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實係咪應該長期keep住滴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n正常一個月先可以滴一次 毒藥黎 唔可以比貓脷到"},{"pid":"eac90c036d13f9133feaad100bbbc5b5a20b81b2","tid":226871,"uid":9863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T22:35:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實係咪應該長期keep住滴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n正常一個月先可以滴一次 毒藥黎 唔可以比貓脷到</blockquote><br />\n我意思係 係咪要每個月滴滴一世"},{"pid":"a8dd429834069a70b389a7c0b4d6b9cfa9701bf1","tid":226871,"uid":985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T22:49:05.000Z","msg":"正常屋企好乾淨，鞋都唔入屋既，唔滴都無所謂。<br />\n我自己就3個月1次(感覺上好過無滴)<br />\n個個用滴rev，一黎貴，二黎始終都係藥.<br />\n而家一盒好似賣緊240"},{"pid":"563709916f141a900fb01aa2602d4d4ebef4f63a","tid":226871,"uid":107742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T22:53:58.000Z","msg":"點解可以養到有蝨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efbfe2c4c9840c38795592a0bbcb73953c1b4d58","tid":226871,"uid":37505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T23:06:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解可以養到有蝨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同問，帶過出街？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9570f58b190361e2c53986f719cd43ebf70f9abf","tid":226871,"uid":14090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T00:30:58.000Z","msg":"屋企清清佢好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 隻貓身上有咁多 代表屋企仲有勁多<br />\n<br />\nBtw 睇睇下圖覺得成身都好痕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba087d976f26326310c3eda3abc97c9d3760f4f3","tid":226871,"uid":47819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T00:38:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實係咪應該長期keep住滴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n想知，同問</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔使<br />\n其實清哂就可以停<br />\n無必要唔需要滴<br />\n有既話即刻滴番<br />\n<br />\n黑色識郁係蚤<br />\n黑色唔識郁果d 蚤屎<br />\n仔細睇<br />\n仲有蚤蛋<br />\n同埋d 好細微既蚤蟲仔 呢兩者都係好細好細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （同好核突<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n<br />\nBtw 你個fd肯定無滴藥水<br />\n如果唔係唔會咁多<br />\n咬死d貓啦"},{"pid":"cb6175c60854b166cc87a1e50cfc23a3c8d553f3","tid":226871,"uid":65935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T01:50:04.000Z","msg":"快撚啲帶佢出去比人沖涼啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />上次我隻貓又係咁，快手睇下屋企有冇啲半透明嘅貓蝨卵，有嘅快啲用吸塵機吸走曬去，唔係你全家都好撚大獲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上次搞左我兩個月先殺得晒啲貓蝨，咬到我成隻腳，起碼起左5,60粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"221ac9de55a9e894b680bac478b2c5b73d6f2092","tid":226871,"uid":83128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T02:11:39.000Z","msg":"我隻貓有成半年冇滴過 但最近帶佢去睇醫生都話佢好乾淨，會唔會係你朋友屋企衛生環境唔好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b6611b55a8edbde2d5b1aa1acb8aa97143e0c0f","tid":226871,"uid":83128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T02:13:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我隻貓有成半年冇滴過 但最近帶佢去睇醫生都話佢好乾淨，會唔會係你朋友屋企衛生環境唔好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n利申：會一星期幫佢抹一次身"},{"pid":"f3ff96909138e8819380b6f4c86c3b43e0edd088","tid":226871,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T02:17:56.000Z","msg":"扮幫fd問唔使俾人屌？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}